{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"93a1aae6bb","title":"李富春给全国总工会四个组织的信","origin":"1967年4月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（3）》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"362fcd0fde","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":3,"articleId":"93a1aae6bb"}],"tags":[{"id":"25e2abfb25","name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"b3c50bb47c","name":"刘宁一","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9c4175f9ee","name":"李富春"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a066135c94","type":"title","text":"李富春给全国总工会四个组织的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"41e7df0014","type":"authors","text":"李富春","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"a4175ff830","type":"appellation","text":"中华全国总工会工人文工团、毛泽东思想红卫兵、毛泽东思想宣传队、红旗公社、中华全国总工会机关《国际红旗》公社、革命的同志们：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"0c3fdeed3f","type":"paragraph","text":"看了你们二月二十八日的信和“红旗”第一期，我和康生同志有下列意见向你们建议：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"d4a48bffa9","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）刘宁一同志，中央认为不是“三反分子”。因此，你们的“红旗”第一期材料不能公开散发。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"52282bb986","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）你们不能把马纯古等人所谓揭露刘宁一同志的材料，作为你们的材料，来揭露刘宁一。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"bb4a36e4eb","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）希望你们好好学习《红旗》杂志四期社论，和人民日报发表的《我们鲁迅兵团向何处去？》等重要文章，来提高政策水平。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"4815bbecda","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）你们的报刊不要用”红旗”的名义，以免与中央的红旗杂志混淆起来。等待你们把文件学完后再找你们。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"13bcfbf3ba","type":"appellation","text":"无产阶级文化革命敬礼！","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"bc000d97d9","type":"paragraph","text":" 富春三月三日","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"}],"page":{"id":"820c5e247a","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"93a1aae6bb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}